Privacy Policy
Last Updated: [7-5-2025]

This Privacy Policy describes how the mobile application ("the App") developed by MoLoN LaVe handles your information.

1. Information We Collect
MoLoN LaVe does not collect, store, or process any personal data directly through the App. We do not require users to register, sign in, or submit any personally identifiable information.

2. Third-Party Advertising & Tracking
The App displays ads provided by third-party advertising networks. These services may collect data independently of MoLoN LaVe for the purpose of delivering relevant or personalized advertisements.

Information these third parties may collect includes:

Advertising identifiers (e.g., IDFA, GAID)

IP address

Device information (OS, language, model)

App usage data

Location (if permitted by the OS)

MoLoN LaVe does not access or control this data and is not responsible for how third parties use it. Please refer to their privacy policies for more information.

3. Advertising Partners
Our app may integrate with the following ad networks:

Google AdMob

Unity Ads

AppLovin

These partners may use cookies or similar technologies to collect information for ad personalization and analytics. You can opt out of personalized advertising through your device settings or the links provided in each policy.

4. Your Rights
Although MoLoN LaVe does not collect personal information directly, users may have the right to:

Request access to or deletion of data collected by third-party services.

Opt out of personalized advertising via device settings or third-party platforms.

Contact third-party providers directly regarding their data practices.

5. Children‚Äôs Privacy
This App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If we become aware that such data has been collected inadvertently, we will take immediate steps to delete it.

